MesgHUB
=======

|pypi|

What is this?
-------------

MesgHUB is an mail service for debug internet applications, supporting Python 2.7.
It includes module for many different purposes.

Installing
----------

To install the latest version of MesgHUB using pip::

  $ pip install mesghub
